---
---
<section class="hero" id="top">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <span class="mono">SolutionXL BV · 2018 →</span>
      <span class="availability mono"><span class="dot"></span>Momenteel: voorzitter Regiegroep GrIT — Planning &amp; Resourcing</span>
    </div>

    <p class="eyebrow mono">Senior regie en realisatie in complexe IT- en verandertrajecten</p>

    <h1 class="hero-head">
      Wij nemen<br>
      <span class="it">tijdelijk</span> over<br>
      waar het <span class="it">écht</span><br>
      ingewikkeld<br>
      wordt.
    </h1>

    <p class="hero-sub">
      SolutionXL BV levert tijdelijke senior versterking in <strong>project- en programmaregie</strong>, <strong>product ownership</strong>, <strong>ketenregie</strong> en <strong>release- en implementatiemanagement</strong> — voor opdrachtgevers zoals Defensie, Rainforest Alliance, ABN AMRO, Transavia, Vattenfall en Achmea.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-bottom">
      <p class="quote">
        Werken moet leuk zijn. En: hoe kan ik je helpen?
        <span class="quote-src">— Twee vragen waarmee elke opdracht bij SolutionXL begint</span>
      </p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn">Plan een gesprek <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
        <a href="#diensten" class="btn-alt">Bekijk de diensten ↓</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero { padding-block: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 9rem) clamp(3rem, 8vw, 7rem); position: relative; }

  .hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    color: var(--muted);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .availability {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--accent-2);
  }

  .dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--accent-2);
    border-radius: 999px;
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(1.3); }
  }

  .eyebrow {
    color: var(--accent);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.25rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    max-width: 42rem;
  }

  .hero-head {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 10vw, 10rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 0.94;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .hero-head .it { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.4vw, 1.25rem);
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--ink-2);
    max-width: 54ch;
    margin-top: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
  }
  .hero-sub strong {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent);
    padding-bottom: 1px;
  }

  .hero-bottom {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    margin-top: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    align-items: end;
  }

  .quote {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.2vw, 1.9rem);
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--ink);
    max-width: 26ch;
  }
  .quote::before {
    content: '"';
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 1.5em;
    line-height: 0;
    vertical-align: -0.2em;
    margin-right: 0.1em;
  }
  .quote::after {
    content: '"';
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 1.5em;
    line-height: 0;
    vertical-align: -0.4em;
  }

  .quote-src {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .hero-bottom { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
  }
</style>
